get.description:
Get available time slots grouped by date for better user experience
Example response:
{
  "2024-12-10": [
    {"slot_id": 1, "time": "09:00 AM", "available": 30, "capacity": 30},
    {"slot_id": 2, "time": "02:00 PM", "available": 25, "capacity": 30}
  ],
  "2024-12-11": [...]
}

